snippet.title: Mythic Origins | Announce Trailer [Free Prologue for Mythic]
snippet.description:
Play for free July 14th.
Wishlist now on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2018990/Mythic_Origins/

Discord: https://discord.gg/mythicgame

Linktree: https://linktr.ee/MythicGame

Mythic Origins is the free prequel to Mythic - a Roguelite MMO where you explore an infinite, procedurally generated labyrinth. Discover a world packed with puzzles, enemies, bosses, and treasure. Join forces with fellow heroes to hunt down the gods, or strike out alone and be the first to discover uncharted territory. Become Mythic.
